.description
Multifunctional commodity for OS 2.0.  Includes windowactivator,
time-display in several modes and formats, alarm function,
KeyStroke-Clicker, time to environment, Window/ Screen cycling, LeftyMouse,
ESC-Key can close Windows, Revision Control System, telefone bill
calculator, Screen/Mouse-Blanker, Mapping of german "Umlauts", PopUp Shell,
AppIcon support, LeftyMouse, user definable HotKeys.  Fully controllable
via ARexx-Port.  All settings can be customized and saved to disk.
Requires OS 2.0.  Written in assembly for speed and efficiency.  
